<subSubSection id="2DF0ACA1FFFFFFC0FF71FE08FBAEFD2A" pageId="23" pageNumber="24" type="description">
<paragraph id="6555FF2AFFFFFFC0FF71FE08FAD8FDB7" blockId="23.[151,1437,438,645]" pageId="23" pageNumber="24">
(
<figureCitation id="FDD1E3AFFFFFFFC0FF79FE08FF04FE5B" box="[159,249,474,501]" captionStart="FIGURE 15" captionStartId="68.[151,250,1966,1990]" captionTargetBox="[218,1370,191,1934]" captionTargetId="figure-32@68.[208,1379,181,1943]" captionTargetPageId="68" captionText="FIGURE 15. Eudocima paulii and Eudocima phalonia group adults (dorsal aspect)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6605537" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6605537/files/figure.png" pageId="23" pageNumber="24">Figs 15</figureCitation>
: E–F, 21: H, 27: A–D, 32: J, 33: G–H, N–O, 34: I–J, 35: I–J, 36: H, 37: E–F, J–K, 38: J–L, 40: C–D, 42: B–C, E–F, 44: H, 45: A, 46: I, 47: J–K, 48: D–E, 51: D–E, 53: D–E, 55: D–E, 57: C–E, 58: D, H, 92: B)
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="6555FF2AFFFFFFC0FF71FDF0FBAEFD2A" blockId="23.[151,1437,438,645]" pageId="23" pageNumber="24">
The diagnosis is covered in the 
<taxonomicName id="A2EA84A9FFFFFFC0FE12FDF1FD8CFD92" authorityName="Borth &amp; Kons" authorityYear="2021" box="[500,625,546,572]" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Eudocima" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="23" pageNumber="24" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="afrikana">
<emphasis id="579E2338FFFFFFC0FE12FDF1FD8CFD92" box="[500,625,546,572]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="24">E. afrikana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
description. It is found from east central Africa to 
<collectingCountry id="1DFDBFBAFFFFFFC0FB79FDF0FACDFD92" box="[1183,1328,546,572]" name="South Africa" pageId="23" pageNumber="24">South Africa</collectingCountry>
. The only other mainland African 
<taxonomicName id="A2EA84A9FFFFFFC0FE43FD94FDEAFDCE" box="[421,535,582,608]" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Eudocima" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="23" pageNumber="24" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="579E2338FFFFFFC0FE43FD94FDEAFDCE" box="[421,535,582,608]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="24">Eudocima</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
besides 
<taxonomicName id="A2EA84A9FFFFFFC0FD9FFD95FD05FDCE" authorityName="Borth &amp; Kons" authorityYear="2021" box="[633,760,582,608]" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Eudocima" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="23" pageNumber="24" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="afrikana">
<emphasis id="579E2338FFFFFFC0FD9FFD95FD05FDCE" box="[633,760,582,608]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="24">E. afrikana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
are 
<taxonomicName id="A2EA84A9FFFFFFC0FCCDFD95FC56FDCE" baseAuthorityName="Walker" baseAuthorityYear="1869" box="[811,939,582,608]" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Eudocima" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="23" pageNumber="24" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="divitiosa">
<emphasis id="579E2338FFFFFFC0FCCDFD95FC56FDCE" box="[811,939,582,608]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="24">E. divitiosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<emphasis id="579E2338FFFFFFC0FC02FD95FAB7FDCE" box="[996,1354,582,608]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="24">
<taxonomicName id="A2EA84A9FFFFFFC0FC02FD95FB98FDCE" baseAuthorityName="Linnaeus" baseAuthorityYear="1767" box="[996,1125,583,608]" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Eudocima" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="23" pageNumber="24" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="materna">E. materna</taxonomicName>
. 
<taxonomicName id="A2EA84A9FFFFFFC0FB97FD94FAB7FDCE" baseAuthorityName="Walker" baseAuthorityYear="1869" box="[1137,1354,582,608]" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Eudocima" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="23" pageNumber="24" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="divitiosa">Eudocima divitiosa</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
has no hindwing medial patch, and in 
<taxonomicName id="A2EA84A9FFFFFFC0FE14FDB9FD93FD2A" baseAuthorityName="Linnaeus" baseAuthorityYear="1767" box="[498,622,619,644]" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Eudocima" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="23" pageNumber="24" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="materna">
<emphasis id="579E2338FFFFFFC0FE14FDB9FD93FD2A" box="[498,622,619,644]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="24">E. materna</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
the medial patch is reduced to a round dot.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
